CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 30, 2013

[Cite as 12/30/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-Ohio-5764.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-1652. State v. Rogers.

Cuyahoga App. Nos. 98292, 98584, 98585, 98586, 98587, 98588, 98589, and 98590, 2013-Ohio-3235. This cause is pending before the court as a jurisdictional appeal.

Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to remove appointed attorney Ruth Fischbein-Cohen as counsel of record, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
